<plot>While the Nazi party rises to power, a girl from Berlin is sent to safety. But the enemy catches up with her in her new home country. Her happy life in a foster family ends abruptly when they are all summoned to report to a concentration camp. Collaborators, helpers, resistance workers and bystanders all play their part in this beautifully filmed docu/drama, which sees the girl miraculously survive. But others are less lucky.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?656254</url></doc>
